{"data":[{"id":562755561,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562755561","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546142406,"updated_time":1546142406,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e瓜还没熟透，闲聊几句…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e网络上嘲讽之声不绝于耳，还编出了各种类似问题…不是说不能质疑题主的能力，但是他的证明还没公布就冷嘲热讽，这种现象和题主吊众人胃口一样，都不是什么值得鼓励的事情…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我只是觉得题主真正让人嗤鼻的是他故意卖关子…（阿提亚爵士也做过这事，但他是在会议上公布，合情合理啊…）当然，这一举动也说明，他还不是个民科，因为后者巴不得尽早得到他人认可，尤其是金字塔顶端那些人的认可，而题主却想把证明先丢给金字塔中下层的这群人…这么看来，他不过是个不懂事的孩子…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这件事里，孩子没有孩子的样子，大人也没有大人的样子…但孩子终究是孩子，他的时间还长的很，还有大把机会纠正错误…大人们呢…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一次说了这么多人，匿名了…\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561375849,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"03e456185f50a24d079d5e711a8c9d05","url_token":"zheng-le-86-98","name":"郑乐","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f8ae07bfc47004e541f9d9489b721169_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f8ae07bfc47004e541f9d9489b721169_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/03e456185f50a24d079d5e711a8c9d05","user_type":"people","headline":"热爱历史法律军事哲学的天然气工程师。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561375849","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545963197,"updated_time":1545963197,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e第一，你的表述都有问题，应该是会被保送清华北大数学系吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e第二，你没见识，比清华北大数学系牛逼的多了去了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e第三，我敢断定你连看懂哥德巴赫猜想都成问题，更别说证明了。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560584265,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3e31ed1e6a41e96a8928255e6c28736e","url_token":"da-nao-zheng-chang-ren","name":"大脑正常人","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-45dd1977cc80d9246ee13abbbb21e51f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-45dd1977cc80d9246ee13abbbb21e51f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3e31ed1e6a41e96a8928255e6c28736e","user_type":"people","headline":"科普狂犬病知识","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560584265","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545871481,"updated_time":1545871583,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e假设真有这等事的话，那不是保送的问题，而是直接当清华数学系主任都有富裕！题主这问题类似问一个战胜阿法狗的人有没资格免选直接打围甲一样    \u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560467611,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1fcaaa4f7c0453c6504a335f7ce0bc60","url_token":"deng-deng-xiao-tian-shi-w","name":"等等小天使w","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1fcaaa4f7c0453c6504a335f7ce0bc60","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560467611","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545840091,"updated_time":1545840091,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我觉得如果大家如果觉得不相信或者想要防止他民科的人至少不要冷嘲热讽吧，这不是更加容易误导吗？况且青春期孩子就是越嘲讽越叛逆的啊?...至少我从这些回答里看出来了一些看热闹的以及以正义为名的嘲讽。现实固然很残酷，但言语有时更伤人。不要觉得嘲讽两句就能让谁痛改前非，还是让事实说话。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560964320,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"61cef0ce9a5d7de31295c04610afc85a","url_token":"mo-xiu-68-86","name":"墨修","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-25926f1cb60e6ba79b37019a17fce673_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-25926f1cb60e6ba79b37019a17fce673_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/61cef0ce9a5d7de31295c04610afc85a","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560964320","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545902694,"updated_time":1545902694,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我很奇怪，只是有一个高中生说自己证明了哥德巴赫猜想并准备公布，为什么会有这么人批判他？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e请问他是打扰你了嘛？他是抢了你证明的机会吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他只是想发表自己的证明，为什么要去骂他呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e恕我直言，骂他的人相当一部分可能连哥德巴赫猜想的真正内容都不知道。骂他，只是他们自以为是的认为高中生不可能做到这点，认为这人在吸引别人的目光而已。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你凭什么认为他就一定做不到了？？？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只是因为他年龄小？只是因为你自以为是的认定？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e安心的当个吃瓜群众不行吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个新星，无论它将在短暂灿烂之后陨落，又或是成功冉冉升起，能否对它努力去燃烧的过程表示该有的敬意？？？？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你认为你自己不行，请别认为所有人都不行。哪怕最后证明他是错的，能不能不要站在自以为是的制高点上批判他？毕竟，你连尝试的勇气都未曾拥有。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562646940,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"79a2c2975d8dd0af4b324b22b35d4058","url_token":"zhu-ce-17-70","name":"I-邽山穷奇","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-11619b5f707bb2bbf3aeb9b0dc817561_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-11619b5f707bb2bbf3aeb9b0dc817561_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/79a2c2975d8dd0af4b324b22b35d4058","user_type":"people","headline":"男儿何不带吴钩，收取关山五十州","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562646940","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-46c36bf68daade52dc436e97373d2c37_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546129939,"updated_time":1546142265,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e耽搁我期末考试的时间吃瓜\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e要是瓜不甜，我就打死你\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-46c36bf68daade52dc436e97373d2c37_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"68