56b64d77370f3c17de1650bfb384_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561808071,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b144c9f2feadfa399a2603f7b1b4912e","url_token":"ding-chun-88","name":"定春","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/24c264d44_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/24c264d44_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b144c9f2feadfa399a2603f7b1b4912e","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561808071","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546003099,"updated_time":1546139690,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我是个文科生，数学最多只学到微积分入门，不过我觉得这个问题用我们专业的话来说大概就是：如果高中生能获得诺贝尔文学奖，会被北大中文系保送吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e————————————————————————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2018.12.30改：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果高中生能破译所有甲骨文，会被北大中文系保送吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e被大家提醒了，诺奖并不是一个具体的科研成果，况且还是文学奖（丘吉尔还拿过文学奖），放在这里与哥德巴赫猜想比较不合适。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说到甲骨文，前几年媒体吹捧的“高考甲骨文考生”后续在这里：\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baijiahao.baidu.com/s%3Fid%3D1574423329106964%26wfr%3Dspider%26for%3Dpc\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e当年被破格录取的“甲骨文”作文考生, 你知道如今怎么样了吗?\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e导师何崝：心静浮躁 吹起牛来比谁都厉害\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e这个两年中，感觉到他学校不是很踏实的。他就不是这块料，不是做学问的，非常浮躁。他吹起牛来比谁都厉害，很多书他都说读过了。像这样的一个学风，我们怎么能容忍呢?他在这个甲骨文方面还不是非常的突出。他只是认识一些甲骨文，好像是几百个吧。我们找一个中学生，培养他一两个月，他基本上就可以认识上千个甲骨文了。这个并不是什么大不了的事情。\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e如今泯然众人矣的黄蛉说：当初在高考的时候用甲骨文来写作文其实也只是逞一时之快，因为知道自己的成绩或许连本科都上不了，索性就破罐子破摔，让阅卷老师看看自己平时所学的不一样的东西，结果没想到反而因祸得福！\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e媒体舆论把“怪才”黄蛉推上了高峰，阴差阳错的社会又给了他让人羡慕的“特殊待遇”，可悲可叹，才学和性情却不与时俱进，最终还是被社会否定！简直是现代版《伤仲永》！\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561751681,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561751681","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545996287,"updated_time":1545996867,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e当然。前提是你能真的证明出来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实，平时没事时证明玩玩也没什么，不要担心被人说“民科”。在试图证明的过程里，你可以学到很多东西。肯定也会多方查阅这方面的资料，学到很多知识。为了了解那些知识和证明途径，你会主动去学些东西，认识到不足，也许最后你知难而退，但是你会因此学到很多东西。民科的讨厌其实不在于其业余研究本身，而是因为其中的很多人妄自尊大，对于知识过于傲慢，思维能力不足又不愿意承认，不去努力改善，对待知识不够谦逊，甚至有时明知道自己错了还要硬凹，把面子摆在知识的前面，等等。很多人并非真正讨厌民科，只是讨厌那种非理性的精神偏执，讨厌的是以天才自居而又拿不出真本事。否则的话，人人都有研究科学及数学的自由，不管你处于科学共同体的官方机构，还是业余爱好者。而旁观者，也最好不要动辄用“民科”这种贴标签、扣帽子的行为，一上来就对人做定性的否定，就好像知乎有些真正的科学回答，反被某些人一上来就骂“民科”，结果最后自己被打脸了。如果对方错了，可以实事求是指出错在哪里，就事论事，而不要一上来就扣民科的帽子，这行为很不好，并非真正的科学态度。总之，你要有兴趣证明，可以玩玩去，利用这个学点东西也是很好的。有些东西你要真的实践了，才知道真正问题所在。但一定要保持对知识的谦逊、开放态度，热衷于学习相关知识，准备工作要做好，多看点相关资料，不要急于图成。也许你原本要证明哥德巴赫猜想，结果在这过程里找到另外的更值得奋斗、也更为“现实”的目标及相关发现，也未可知。很多东西的发现是要由兴趣来驱动，不管你最初的兴趣是什么，至少要有一个兴趣，兴趣是一个切入点和引导，把你引向某个领域及相关联领域，使你真正沉浸进入。就好比我从小对女性身体感兴趣，现在我成了一个兽医（咳咳）。。。是怎么七转八转最终进入这领域的，一言难尽。但绝对是最初那一神秘的、看似不相关的兴趣作为最初驱动。。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561713677,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"be1b3eb3b1cefb4b66ef029a27f34443","url_token":"pu-pu-pu-68-82","name":"噗噗噗","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/be1b3eb3b1cefb4b66ef029a27f34443","user_type":"people","headline":"学生党","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561713677","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545991976,"updated_time":1545991976,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e兄弟，他们都不赞同你，但我知道，你是从异世界穿越过来的天才数学家！只不过是因为意外才附身到这个世界的一个普通高中生身上，我支持你！只求你日后功成名就重回巅峰的时候能想起我，让我喝口汤！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561695219,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561695219","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545990072,"updated_time":1545990072,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e清华北大校长马上会动用私人关系限制你出境：这样的人才千万不能让哈佛抢了去。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561653890,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4d1a457631bf6b65af6019314cbf10ab","url_token":"li-yihui-7","name":"Cp一飞","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/e39a00fea507ac172d7226a4a47b00ed_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/e39a00fea507ac172d7226a4a47b00ed_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/4d1a457631bf6b65af6019314cbf10ab","user_type":"people","headline":"假的大学狗","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561653890","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545986517,"updated_time":1545986863,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我觉得你们都错怪他了，可不可以一上来就不要抵制人家，而是去寻思背后的合理性。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e经观察提问者的知乎“历程”，我觉得，走常规路对于他来说已经是不可能了，因为就用2个月时间把哥德巴赫猜想给弄出来，肯定不是他能做出来了。那，他不是“他”不就好了，提问者想必是未来自己研制出的time machine ，为了一雪高考之耻，专门回到2018来，给诸位送上19年的开篇大礼。我觉得，也只有这么解释合理了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外，我将在一月三日公布股市百分百预测函数模型，望大家多多关注！（狗头）\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=780\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=740\u0026sort_by=default","totals":1823}}
